---
title: Greek-Inspired Breaded Chicken Tenders with Potato Wedges and Garlic-Feta Green Beans
description: Greek-style spiced chicken, savoury roasted potato wedges and tzatziki sauce are the stars of this dinner. Don't forget the garlic-feta topped green beans to round it all out!
